Homepage: https://github.com/aliheba125/repo
Description: Dragon repository tool manager
 Beautiful terminal UI to browse (numbered), search, install by number/name/
 range/all, update and remove the Dragon repository tools on Termux. Type
 'dragon' for the looping interactive menu, or 'dragon help' for commands.
